PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Antonio Demond WATKINS, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 159578
COA: 346767 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 24, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of defendant-appellant to extend the time for filing his reply is GRANTED. The reply submitted on July 18, 2019, is accepted as timely filed.
